description:
RlfProfile: Table containing Radio Link Failure (RLF) profile parameters for different cells.

dateTime: Timestamp of RLF profile data.
Area_Name: Geographical area of the cell.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier.
Id3: Redundant profile identifier.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
RlfProfile.t301: Parameter t301 (likely related to RLF timer).
RlfProfile.n310: Parameter n310 (likely related to RLF counter).
RlfProfile.n311: Parameter n311 (likely related to RLF counter).
RlfProfile.rlfProfileId: Unique identifier of the RLF profile.
RlfProfile.reservedBy: Information about the entity reserving this RLF profile.
RlfProfile.t311: Parameter t311 (likely related to RLF timer).
RlfProfile.t310: Parameter t310 (likely related to RLF timer).
